== 死亡经过 ==
就在莉拉·奥尔康决定在2014年12月28日自杀前，她就已经设定好将自己的遗书在当天下午5:30发送到自己的[[Tumblr|Tumblr]]账户上。<ref name=Coolidge /> 在她的遗书里，她表示她将结束自己的生命，并评论道：
{{quote|我已经决定，一切已经够了。即便我搬离这个家庭，我也无法成功重整我的性别。我永远不会满意于我的样貌和声音。我永远不会有足够的朋友来满足我。我也永远不会有足够的爱来满足我。我永远不会找到一个爱我的人。我永远不会快乐。我余下的生命里将像一个孤独的男人，我希望自己是一个女人，或者说我将像一个孤独的女人在自怨自艾。没有胜利。没有出路。我已经很伤心，我不需要我的生活变得更加糟糕。人们说“它将变得更好”，但在我的生命里，这是错误的。它只会变得更糟。每天我都变得更糟。这就是一切的原因，这就是我要自杀的原因。对不起，如果这不是个足够好的理由，但对我来说却足矣。<ref>原文：I have decided I've had enough. I'm never going to transition successfully, even when I move out. I'm never going to be happy with the way I look or sound. I'm never going to have enough friends to satisfy me. I'm never going to have enough love to satisfy me. I'm never going to find a man who loves me. I'm never going to be happy. Either I live the rest of my life as a lonely man who wishes he were a woman or I live my life as a lonelier woman who hates herself. There's no winning. There's no way out. I'm sad enough already, I don't need my life to get any worse. People say "it gets better" but that isn't true in my case. It gets worse. Each day I get worse. That's the gist of it, that's why I feel like killing myself. Sorry if that's not a good enough reason for you, it's good enough for me.</ref><ref name=note/>}}

在她的遗书里，她表示希望将自己的遗产捐赠给一个支持跨性别人士的慈善机构，并呼吁在学校教授[[性别认同|性别认同]]的内容。<ref name=note/><ref name=BostonGlobe /> 这封遗书最后以“我的死必须意味着一些什么。我的死将被计入今年自杀的跨性别人士统计数字里。我希望当有人看到这个数字的时候能说‘（我们）搞砸了’并挽救它。请救救这个社会！”结尾。<ref name=note/><ref name=BostonGlobe /><ref name=Buncombe>{{cite news |title=Leelah Alcorn suicide: petition calls for transgender teenager's chosen name to be used on her tombstone |newspaper=The Independent |first=Andrew |last=Buncombe |date=2015-01-01|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/leelah-alcorn-suicide-petition-calls-for-transgender-teenagers-chosen-name-to-be-used-on-her-tombstone-9953239.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Y5Hfyxq5?url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/leelah-alcorn-suicide-petition-calls-for-transgender-teenagers-chosen-name-to-be-used-on-her-tombstone-9953239.html |archivedate=2015-04-26|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2017-06-23}}</ref> 随后，奥尔康的第二封以“对不起”为标题的帖子也随即发出。在这篇帖子里，她向自己的密友和兄弟姐妹道歉，表示自己的自杀将会给他们带去痛苦。同时她也在这里对自己的父母表示道，“肏！你不能像这样控制别人！这很糟糕！”<ref name=note/><ref>{{cite web |title=Transgender Teen Leelah Alcorn Left A Strong Message In Her Sorry Note For Friends & Family – Read It HERE |first=Perez |last=Hilton |website=PerezHilton.com |date=2014-12-31|url=http://perezhilton.com/2014-12-31-transgender-teen-leelah-alcorn-left-sorry-note-friends-fuck-you-mom-dad#.VKcSK9KsWSo |archivedate=2015-06-08|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Z8r7JEmZ?url=http://perezhilton.com/2014-12-31-transgender-teen-leelah-alcorn-left-sorry-note-friends-fuck-you-mom-dad |deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Transgender teen asks for her suicide to 'mean something' and 'fix society' |date=2014-12-31|url=http://rt.com/usa/219115-teen-suicide-note-transgender-awareness/ |website=RT |accessdate=2015-10-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150102134010/http://rt.com/usa/219115-teen-suicide-note-transgender-awareness/ |archivedate=2015-01-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Mom of Ohio transgender teen who took her own life says she did not 'support' child's gender change |first=David |last=Boroff |date=2015-01-02|website=The New York Times |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/mom-transgender-teen-killed-speaks-article-1.2063698 |accessdate=2015-10-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328233259/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/mom-transgender-teen-killed-speaks-article-1.2063698 |archivedate=2015-03-28}}</ref> 此外，在莉拉·奥尔康的床头还发现了一封由她手写的“我已经受够了”的遗书。但是这份遗书在警方复印之后就被她的母亲丢弃了。<ref name="investigation" />

12月28日凌晨，警方通告新闻媒体，在莉拉·奥尔康被撞击身亡之前，她正在靠近{{Link-en|联盟镇 (俄亥俄州沃伦县)|Union Township, Warren County, Ohio|联盟镇}}的[[71号州际公路|71号州际公路]]路段向南行走；在凌晨2:30左右，她在南莱巴嫩出口附近被一辆半拖车撞到。<ref name=Cuncinnati>{{cite web |author=Molski, Henry |url=http://www.cincinnati.com/story/news/2014/12/28/boy-killed-by-truck-on-71/20968865/ |title=Boy, 17, hit and killed by semi on I-71 |website=Cincinnati.com |accessdate=2014-12-30|date=2014-12-30|dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130000737/http://www.cincinnati.com/story/news/2014/12/28/boy-killed-by-truck-on-71/20968865/ |archivedate=2017-01-30 }}</ref> 莉拉·奥尔康当场死亡。据信，莉拉·奥尔康从她父母位于金斯米尔斯的家中出走三到四公里之后才被撞击身亡。<ref name=LGBTNation>{{cite web |url=http://www.lgbtqnation.com/2014/12/transgender-teen-struck-and-killed-on-ohio-interstate-in-apparent-suicide/ |title=Transgender teen struck and killed on Ohio interstate in apparent suicide |work=LGBTQ Nation |date=2014-12-29 |accessdate=2015-10-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323175604/https://www.lgbtqnation.com/2014/12/transgender-teen-struck-and-killed-on-ohio-interstate-in-apparent-suicide/ |archivedate=2016-03-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 事发后，高速公路因此封闭了一个小时。<ref name=Coolidge/> {{Link-en|俄亥俄州高速公路巡逻队|Ohio State Highway Patrol}}很快就此展开了调查，<ref name=Cuncinnati /> 奥尔康的尸体也被送往[[蒙哥马利县_(俄亥俄州)|蒙哥马利县]]验尸官那里接受解剖。<ref name=Coolidge /> 事故当中，开车司机并没有受伤。<ref name=RT />

这份遗书发布48小时之内，在Tumblr上共吸引82,272次点阅；<ref name=Coolidge /> 而到了12月31日上午，这份遗书被转载多达200,000次。<ref name=BostonGlobe/> 为《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》撰稿的记者莫拉·约翰斯顿（{{lang|en|Maura Johnston}}）形容这是一个“热帖”。<ref name=BostonGlobe>{{cite web |last1=Johnston |first1=Maura |title=Transgender teen Leelah Alcorn: ‘My death needs to mean something’ |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/2014/12/31/transgender-teen-leelah-alcorn-death-needs-mean-something/4hw6uPd8NtjIbn8kAdyAbM/story.html |website=The Boston Globe |accessdate=2015-01-01|date=2014-12-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XgyFtn2k?url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/lifestyle/2014/12/31/transgender-teen-leelah-alcorn-death-needs-mean-something/4hw6uPd8NtjIbn8kAdyAbM/story.html |archivedate=2015-04-10|deadurl=yes}}</ref> 但这封遗书在奥尔康父母的要求下被Tumblr移除，<ref name=note2>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/leelah-alcorns-parents-had-tumblr-suicide-note-deleted-transgender-teen-mourned-high-1773000|title=Leelah Alcorn's Parents Had Tumblr Suicide Note Deleted; Transgender Teen Mourned At High School|first=Maria|last=Vultaggio|date=2015-01-04|website=International Business Times|accessdate=2015-01-06|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314140028/http://www.ibtimes.com/leelah-alcorns-parents-had-tumblr-suicide-note-deleted-transgender-teen-mourned-high-1773000|archivedate=2016-03-14}}</ref> 同时莉拉·奥尔康的博客也变成公众无法阅读的状态。<ref name=blog>{{cite web|url=http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2015/01/03/leelah-alcorns-blog-and-suicide-note-deleted-from-tumblr/|title=Leelah Alcorn's blog and suicide note deleted from Tumblr|first=Nick|last=Duffy|date=2015-01-03|website=PinkNews|accessdate=2015-01-06|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621142209/http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2015/01/03/leelah-alcorns-blog-and-suicide-note-deleted-from-tumblr/|archivedate=2016-06-12}}</ref> 根据奥尔康的家庭牧师宣称，奥尔康家族在收到威胁之后决定私下进行葬礼。<ref name=funeral1>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/funeral-transgender-teen-leelah-alcorn-moved-because-threats-n278541|title=Funeral for Transgender Teen Leelah Alcorn Moved Because of 'Threats'|first1=Elisha|last1=Fieldstadt|first2=Scott|last2=Newell|date=2015-01-02|website=[[NBC新闻|NBC新闻]]|accessdate=2015-01-03|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316051406/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/funeral-transgender-teen-leelah-alcorn-moved-because-threats-n278541|archivedate=2017-03-16}}</ref> 据报道，奥尔康的遗体是被火化的。<ref name=funeral1 /> 俄亥俄州巡逻队在2015年4月30日完成对莉拉·奥尔康撞击事故的调查，并裁定莉拉為自杀。<ref name="investigation" />

